{
  "stem": "23622.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And every morning at 5 or 6 o'clock, there was appel in the very cold, cold weather.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he survived that camp and the hard work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was once beaten, too, because it was so cold-- oh, then they went to another concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they had to bring cement, bags of cement, to-- carrying, not on-- on a wheelbarrow-- carrying from one place to the other.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were working, and worked for air-- airfields, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't remember what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But it was the idea that they had to carry those 50 pounds of bags, and sometimes on the bare feet or whatever.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Their hands were more blood then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But they had to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was so cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they think, you know, what we do?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We take the cement bags, and we make like clothes, you know, like put holes for the arms, and we cut out, put our heads.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's not so cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there they put their poor clothes, what they wore, over it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They cover it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they found out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was punishable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They found two.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They found out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they got their punishment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was done in a way that everybody could see it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had to bend over a buckhorse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then the one who beat them, they sang the song.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Every beat, they sang a song, every beat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they had to count the beatings themselves in German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if they make a mistake, they start all over again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But according to my brother, he said the beating was-- the humiliation was worse than the beating.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Humiliated.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Oh, Vucht, I think-- V-U-C-H-T.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was Vucht, that one.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
